              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Other independent evaluation confirms the magnitude of",
                "the result.  Subtracting the primary emitted neutron",
                "with T=1.24+-0.05MeV. K(1)=3.0E-6/(MeV)**2 and",
                "K(2)=6.24E-4/(MeV)**2, from the experimental emission",
                "spectra, then the cross-section of secondary neutron",
                "emission was obtained as about 1280 +- 140 mb. This is",
